{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":931,"text":"Chris Anderson: Christiane,\ngreat to have you here."},{"time":3292,"text":"So you've had this amazing viewpoint,"},{"time":5159,"text":"and perhaps it's fair to say\nthat in the last few years,"},{"time":8243,"text":"there have been some alarming\ndevelopments that you're seeing."},{"time":12020,"text":"What's alarmed you most?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13608,"text":"Christiane Amanpour: Well, just listening\nto the earlier speakers,"},{"time":16824,"text":"I can frame it\nin what they've been saying:"},{"time":19320,"text":"climate change, for instance --\ncities, the threat to our environment"},{"time":22766,"text":"and our lives."},{"time":24440,"text":"It basically also boils down to\nunderstanding the truth"},{"time":28358,"text":"and to be able to get to the truth\nof what we're talking about"},{"time":31393,"text":"in order to really be able to solve it."},{"time":33509,"text":"So if 99.9 percent\nof the science on climate"},{"time":37460,"text":"is empirical, scientific evidence,"},{"time":40541,"text":"but it's competing almost equally\nwith a handful of deniers,"},{"time":45460,"text":"that is not the truth;"},{"time":46711,"text":"that is the epitome of fake news."},{"time":49233,"text":"And so for me, the last few years --\ncertainly this last year --"},{"time":54359,"text":"has crystallized the notion of fake news\nin a way that's truly alarming"},{"time":58643,"text":"and not just some slogan\nto be thrown around."},{"time":61326,"text":"Because when you can't distinguish\nbetween the truth and fake news,"},{"time":65161,"text":"you have a very much more\ndifficult time trying to solve"},{"time":69076,"text":"some of the great issues that we face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72512,"text":"CA: Well, you've been involved\nin this question of,"},{"time":75957,"text":"what is balance, what is truth,\nwhat is impartiality,"},{"time":78893,"text":"for a long time."},{"time":80172,"text":"You were on the front lines\nreporting the Balkan Wars 25 years ago."},{"time":86066,"text":"And back then, you famously said,"},{"time":89502,"text":"by calling out human right abuses,"},{"time":92147,"text":"you said, \"Look, there are some situations\none simply cannot be neutral about,"},{"time":96500,"text":"because when you're neutral,"},{"time":97904,"text":"you are an accomplice.\""},{"time":101243,"text":"So, do you feel that today's journalists\naren't heeding that advice"},{"time":106164,"text":"about balance?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107660,"text":"CA: Well, look, I think for journalists,\nobjectivity is the golden rule."},{"time":111790,"text":"But I think sometimes we don't understand\nwhat objectivity means."},{"time":116230,"text":"And I actually learned this very,\nvery young in my career,"},{"time":119248,"text":"which was during the Balkan Wars."},{"time":120844,"text":"I was young then."},{"time":122084,"text":"It was about 25 years ago."},{"time":124647,"text":"And what we faced was the wholesale\nviolation, not just of human rights,"},{"time":130452,"text":"but all the way to ethnic\ncleansing and genocide,"},{"time":133455,"text":"and that has been adjudicated\nin the highest war crimes court"},{"time":137485,"text":"in the world."},{"time":138673,"text":"So, we know what we were seeing."},{"time":140350,"text":"Trying to tell the world\nwhat we were seeing"},{"time":142911,"text":"brought us accusations of bias,"},{"time":145710,"text":"of siding with one side,"},{"time":147623,"text":"of not seeing the whole side,"},{"time":149509,"text":"and just, you know,\ntrying to tell one story."},{"time":151830,"text":"I particularly and personally\nwas accused of siding with,"},{"time":156161,"text":"for instance, the citizens of Sarajevo --"},{"time":158167,"text":"\"siding with the Muslims,\""},{"time":159618,"text":"because they were the minority\nwho were being attacked"},{"time":162694,"text":"by Christians on the Serb side"},{"time":166456,"text":"in this area."},{"time":168199,"text":"And it worried me."},{"time":169565,"text":"It worried me that I was being\naccused of this."},{"time":171780,"text":"I thought maybe I was wrong,"},{"time":173146,"text":"maybe I'd forgotten what objectivity was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175518,"text":"But then I started to understand\nthat what people wanted"},{"time":178549,"text":"was actually not to do anything --"},{"time":180371,"text":"not to step in,"},{"time":181812,"text":"not to change the situation,"},{"time":183406,"text":"not to find a solution."},{"time":184879,"text":"And so, their fake news at that time,"},{"time":187256,"text":"their lie at that time --"},{"time":188662,"text":"including our government's,\nour democratically elected government's,"},{"time":192216,"text":"with values and principles\nof human rights --"},{"time":194512,"text":"their lie was to say\nthat all sides are equally guilty,"},{"time":198043,"text":"that this has been centuries\nof ethnic hatred,"},{"time":200860,"text":"whereas we knew that wasn't true,"},{"time":202766,"text":"that one side had decided to kill,\nslaughter and ethnically cleanse"},{"time":206437,"text":"another side."},{"time":207618,"text":"So that is where, for me,"},{"time":209138,"text":"I understood that objectivity means\ngiving all sides an equal hearing"},{"time":214468,"text":"and talking to all sides,"},{"time":216597,"text":"but not treating all sides equally,"},{"time":220243,"text":"not creating a forced moral equivalence\nor a factual equivalence."},{"time":225055,"text":"And when you come up against\nthat crisis point"},{"time":229558,"text":"in situations of grave violations\nof international and humanitarian law,"},{"time":235253,"text":"if you don't understand\nwhat you're seeing,"},{"time":237619,"text":"if you don't understand the truth"},{"time":239803,"text":"and if you get trapped\nin the fake news paradigm,"},{"time":243340,"text":"then you are an accomplice."},{"time":245658,"text":"And I refuse to be\nan accomplice to genocide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248679,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":254402,"text":"CH: So there have always been\nthese propaganda battles,"},{"time":257204,"text":"and you were courageous in taking\nthe stand you took back then."},{"time":261652,"text":"Today, there's a whole new way, though,"},{"time":265403,"text":"in which news seems to be becoming fake."},{"time":267631,"text":"How would you characterize that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":269289,"text":"CA: Well, look -- I am really alarmed."},{"time":271397,"text":"And everywhere I look,"},{"time":273623,"text":"you know, we're buffeted by it."},{"time":275484,"text":"Obviously, when the leader\nof the free world,"},{"time":277710,"text":"when the most powerful person\nin the entire world,"},{"time":280207,"text":"which is the president\nof the United States --"},{"time":282477,"text":"this is the most important, most powerful\ncountry in the whole world,"},{"time":287320,"text":"economically, militarily, politically\nin every which way --"},{"time":292415,"text":"and it seeks to, obviously, promote\nits values and power around the world."},{"time":297456,"text":"So we journalists,\nwho only seek the truth --"},{"time":301456,"text":"I mean, that is our mission --"},{"time":303001,"text":"we go around the world\nlooking for the truth"},{"time":305142,"text":"in order to be everybody's eyes and ears,"},{"time":307139,"text":"people who can't go out\nin various parts of the world"},{"time":309682,"text":"to figure out what's going on\nabout things that are vitally important"},{"time":313075,"text":"to everybody's health and security."},{"time":315055,"text":"So when you have a major world leader\naccusing you of fake news,"},{"time":321765,"text":"it has an exponential ripple effect."},{"time":325632,"text":"And what it does is,\nit starts to chip away"},{"time":330472,"text":"at not just our credibility,"},{"time":333384,"text":"but at people's minds --"},{"time":336372,"text":"people who look at us,\nand maybe they're thinking,"},{"time":338760,"text":"\"Well, if the president\nof the United States says that,"},{"time":341453,"text":"maybe somewhere there's a truth in there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":344148,"text":"CH: Presidents have always\nbeen critical of the media --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":348356,"text":"CA: Not in this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349981,"text":"CH: So, to what extent --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351510,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352598,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":355742,"text":"CH: I mean, someone a couple years ago\nlooking at the avalanche of information"},{"time":362662,"text":"pouring through Twitter\nand Facebook and so forth,"},{"time":365922,"text":"might have said,"},{"time":367104,"text":"\"Look, our democracies are healthier\nthan they've ever been."},{"time":369969,"text":"There's more news than ever."},{"time":371514,"text":"Of course presidents\nwill say what they'll say,"},{"time":373749,"text":"but everyone else can say\nwhat they will say."},{"time":376006,"text":"What's not to like?\nHow is there an extra danger?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":380185,"text":"CA: So, I wish that was true."},{"time":382992,"text":"I wish that the proliferation of platforms\nupon which we get our information"},{"time":389109,"text":"meant that there was a proliferation\nof truth and transparency"},{"time":393011,"text":"and depth and accuracy."},{"time":394903,"text":"But I think the opposite has happened."},{"time":397382,"text":"You know, I'm a little bit of a Luddite,"},{"time":399496,"text":"I will confess."},{"time":401147,"text":"Even when we started to talk about\nthe information superhighway,"},{"time":404555,"text":"which was a long time ago,"},{"time":406207,"text":"before social media, Twitter\nand all the rest of it,"},{"time":408882,"text":"I was actually really afraid"},{"time":410730,"text":"that that would put people\ninto certain lanes and tunnels"},{"time":414775,"text":"and have them just focusing\non areas of their own interest"},{"time":419141,"text":"instead of seeing the broad picture."},{"time":421498,"text":"And I'm afraid to say\nthat with algorithms, with logarithms,"},{"time":426108,"text":"with whatever the \"-ithms\" are"},{"time":427780,"text":"that direct us into all these particular\nchannels of information,"},{"time":432070,"text":"that seems to be happening right now."},{"time":433964,"text":"I mean, people have written\nabout this phenomenon."},{"time":436532,"text":"People have said that yes,\nthe internet came,"},{"time":438754,"text":"its promise was to exponentially explode\nour access to more democracy,"},{"time":444521,"text":"more information,"},{"time":446259,"text":"less bias,"},{"time":448175,"text":"more varied information."},{"time":450588,"text":"And, in fact, the opposite has happened."},{"time":452937,"text":"And so that, for me,\nis incredibly dangerous."},{"time":456979,"text":"And again, when you are the president\nof this country and you say things,"},{"time":461518,"text":"it also gives leaders in other\nundemocratic countries the cover"},{"time":468009,"text":"to affront us even worse,"},{"time":470339,"text":"and to really whack us --\nand their own journalists --"},{"time":473223,"text":"with this bludgeon of fake news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"CH: To what extent\nis what happened, though,"},{"time":478208,"text":"in part, just an unintended consequence,"},{"time":480298,"text":"that the traditional\nmedia that you worked in"},{"time":483124,"text":"had this curation-mediation role,"},{"time":485228,"text":"where certain norms were observed,"},{"time":487278,"text":"certain stories would be rejected\nbecause they weren't credible,"},{"time":490455,"text":"but now that the standard\nfor publication and for amplification"},{"time":496978,"text":"is just interest, attention,\nexcitement, click,"},{"time":500330,"text":"\"Did it get clicked on?\""},{"time":501517,"text":"\"Send it out there!\""},{"time":502696,"text":"and that's what's --\nis that part of what's caused the problem?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506224,"text":"CA: I think it's a big problem,\nand we saw this in the election of 2016,"},{"time":509843,"text":"where the idea of \"clickbait\"\nwas very sexy and very attractive,"},{"time":514974,"text":"and so all these fake news sites\nand fake news items"},{"time":519304,"text":"were not just haphazardly\nand by happenstance being put out there,"},{"time":523450,"text":"there's been a whole industry\nin the creation of fake news"},{"time":527925,"text":"in parts of Eastern Europe, wherever,"},{"time":530939,"text":"and you know, it's planted\nin real space and in cyberspace."},{"time":534223,"text":"So I think that, also,"},{"time":536606,"text":"the ability of our technology\nto proliferate this stuff"},{"time":541751,"text":"at the speed of sound\nor light, just about --"},{"time":545286,"text":"we've never faced that before."},{"time":547293,"text":"And we've never faced\nsuch a massive amount of information"},{"time":552184,"text":"which is not curated"},{"time":553773,"text":"by those whose profession\nleads them to abide by the truth,"},{"time":559093,"text":"to fact-check"},{"time":560319,"text":"and to maintain a code of conduct\nand a code of professional ethics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565177,"text":"CH: Many people here may know\npeople who work at Facebook"},{"time":568544,"text":"or Twitter and Google and so on."},{"time":570892,"text":"They all seem like great people\nwith good intention --"},{"time":574048,"text":"let's assume that."},{"time":575452,"text":"If you could speak with the leaders\nof those companies,"},{"time":579151,"text":"what would you say to them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580466,"text":"CA: Well, you know what --"},{"time":582259,"text":"I'm sure they are\nincredibly well-intentioned,"},{"time":584627,"text":"and they certainly developed\nan unbelievable, game-changing system,"},{"time":589869,"text":"where everybody's connected\non this thing called Facebook."},{"time":593104,"text":"And they've created a massive\neconomy for themselves"},{"time":596929,"text":"and an amazing amount of income."},{"time":599633,"text":"I would just say,"},{"time":600837,"text":"\"Guys, you know, it's time\nto wake up and smell the coffee"},{"time":605095,"text":"and look at what's happening\nto us right now.\""},{"time":607821,"text":"Mark Zuckerberg wants to create\na global community."},{"time":610777,"text":"I want to know: What is that global\ncommunity going to look like?"},{"time":614020,"text":"I want to know where the codes\nof conduct actually are."},{"time":618111,"text":"Mark Zuckerberg said --"},{"time":619960,"text":"and I don't blame him,\nhe probably believed this --"},{"time":622702,"text":"that it was crazy to think"},{"time":625082,"text":"that the Russians or anybody else\ncould be tinkering and messing around"},{"time":629215,"text":"with this avenue."},{"time":630482,"text":"And what have we just learned\nin the last few weeks?"},{"time":632988,"text":"That, actually, there has been\na major problem in that regard,"},{"time":635970,"text":"and now they're having to investigate it\nand figure it out."},{"time":639112,"text":"Yes, they're trying to do\nwhat they can now"},{"time":642415,"text":"to prevent the rise of fake news,"},{"time":644597,"text":"but, you know,"},{"time":646004,"text":"it went pretty unrestricted\nfor a long, long time."},{"time":651119,"text":"So I guess I would say, you know,"},{"time":653043,"text":"you guys are brilliant at technology;"},{"time":655166,"text":"let's figure out another algorithm."},{"time":657081,"text":"Can we not?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":658276,"text":"CH: An algorithm that includes\njournalistic investigation --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":661187,"text":"CA: I don't really know how they do it,\nbut somehow, you know --"},{"time":664567,"text":"filter out the crap!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666410,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":667584,"text":"And not just the unintentional --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669610,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":672888,"text":"but the deliberate lies that are planted"},{"time":675118,"text":"by people who've been doing this\nas a matter of warfare"},{"time":679467,"text":"for decades."},{"time":680793,"text":"The Soviets, the Russians --"},{"time":682750,"text":"they are the masters of war\nby other means, of hybrid warfare."},{"time":688618,"text":"And this is a --"},{"time":690689,"text":"this is what they've decided to do."},{"time":693697,"text":"It worked in the United States,"},{"time":695326,"text":"it didn't work in France,"},{"time":696671,"text":"it hasn't worked in Germany."},{"time":698368,"text":"During the elections there,\nwhere they've tried to interfere,"},{"time":701333,"text":"the president of France\nright now, Emmanuel Macron,"},{"time":703959,"text":"took a very tough stand\nand confronted it head on,"},{"time":706506,"text":"as did Angela Merkel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707688,"text":"CH: There's some hope to be had\nfrom some of this, isn't there?"},{"time":710697,"text":"That the world learns."},{"time":711872,"text":"We get fooled once,"},{"time":713214,"text":"maybe we get fooled again,"},{"time":714570,"text":"but maybe not the third time."},{"time":716049,"text":"Is that true?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":717241,"text":"CA: I mean, let's hope."},{"time":718421,"text":"But I think in this regard that so much\nof it is also about technology,"},{"time":721832,"text":"that the technology has to also be given\nsome kind of moral compass."},{"time":725301,"text":"I know I'm talking nonsense,\nbut you know what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":728141,"text":"CH: We need a filter-the-crap algorithm\nwith a moral compass --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":731873,"text":"CA: There you go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733054,"text":"CH: I think that's good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734230,"text":"CA: No -- \"moral technology.\""},{"time":735925,"text":"We all have moral compasses --\nmoral technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739055,"text":"CH: I think that's a great challenge.\nCA: You know what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742058,"text":"CH: Talk just a minute about leadership."},{"time":744026,"text":"You've had a chance to speak\nwith so many people across the world."},{"time":747186,"text":"I think for some of us --"},{"time":748449,"text":"I speak for myself,\nI don't know if others feel this --"},{"time":751165,"text":"there's kind of been a disappointment of:"},{"time":753185,"text":"Where are the leaders?"},{"time":755068,"text":"So many of us have been disappointed --"},{"time":757406,"text":"Aung San Suu Kyi,\nwhat's happened recently,"},{"time":759446,"text":"it's like, \"No! Another one\nbites the dust.\""},{"time":761555,"text":"You know, it's heartbreaking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763178,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":764437,"text":"Who have you met"},{"time":766482,"text":"who you have been\nimpressed by, inspired by?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":769376,"text":"CA: Well, you talk about\nthe world in crisis,"},{"time":771904,"text":"which is absolutely true,"},{"time":773282,"text":"and those of us who spend our whole lives\nimmersed in this crisis --"},{"time":777793,"text":"I mean, we're all on the verge\nof a nervous breakdown."},{"time":780810,"text":"So it's pretty stressful right now."},{"time":783510,"text":"And you're right --"},{"time":784693,"text":"there is this perceived and actual\nvacuum of leadership,"},{"time":787827,"text":"and it's not me saying it,\nI ask all these --"},{"time":790701,"text":"whoever I'm talking to,\nI ask about leadership."},{"time":793178,"text":"I was speaking to the outgoing\npresident of Liberia today,"},{"time":797712,"text":"[Ellen Johnson Sirleaf,]"},{"time":799546,"text":"who --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800724,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":802963,"text":"in three weeks' time,"},{"time":804529,"text":"will be one of the very rare\nheads of an African country"},{"time":808497,"text":"who actually abides by the constitution"},{"time":810699,"text":"and gives up power\nafter her prescribed term."},{"time":814335,"text":"She has said she wants\nto do that as a lesson."},{"time":818216,"text":"But when I asked her about leadership,"},{"time":820272,"text":"and I gave a quick-fire round\nof certain names,"},{"time":822979,"text":"I presented her with the name\nof the new French president,"},{"time":825980,"text":"Emmanuel Macron."},{"time":827437,"text":"And she said --"},{"time":828797,"text":"I said, \"So what do you think\nwhen I say his name?\""},{"time":831327,"text":"And she said,"},{"time":833578,"text":"\"Shaping up potentially to be"},{"time":835927,"text":"a leader to fill our current\nleadership vacuum.\""},{"time":840017,"text":"I thought that was really interesting."},{"time":841874,"text":"Yesterday, I happened to have\nan interview with him."},{"time":844354,"text":"I'm very proud to say,"},{"time":845536,"text":"I got his first international interview.\nIt was great. It was yesterday."},{"time":848979,"text":"And I was really impressed."},{"time":850295,"text":"I don't know whether I should be\nsaying that in an open forum,"},{"time":853247,"text":"but I was really impressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854726,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":856867,"text":"And it could be just because\nit was his first interview,"},{"time":859566,"text":"but -- I asked questions,\nand you know what?"},{"time":861685,"text":"He answered them!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862917,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":864874,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":868167,"text":"There was no spin,"},{"time":869784,"text":"there was no wiggle and waggle,"},{"time":872199,"text":"there was no spend-five-minutes-\nto-come-back-to-the-point."},{"time":875052,"text":"I didn't have to keep interrupting,"},{"time":876744,"text":"which I've become rather\nrenowned for doing,"},{"time":878851,"text":"because I want people\nto answer the question."},{"time":881407,"text":"And he answered me,"},{"time":883482,"text":"and it was pretty interesting."},{"time":886120,"text":"And he said --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887575,"text":"CH: Tell me what he said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889377,"text":"CA: No, no, you go ahead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890621,"text":"CH: You're the interrupter,\nI'm the listener."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892873,"text":"CA: No, no, go ahead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894055,"text":"CH: What'd he say?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":895234,"text":"CA: OK. You've talked about\nnationalism and tribalism here today."},{"time":898336,"text":"I asked him, \"How did you have the guts\nto confront the prevailing winds"},{"time":902122,"text":"of anti-globalization,\nnationalism, populism"},{"time":906681,"text":"when you can see what happened in Brexit,"},{"time":908667,"text":"when you could see what happened\nin the United States"},{"time":911246,"text":"and what might have happened\nin many European elections"},{"time":913865,"text":"at the beginning of 2017?\""},{"time":915606,"text":"And he said,"},{"time":917597,"text":"\"For me, nationalism means war."},{"time":921486,"text":"We have seen it before,"},{"time":923183,"text":"we have lived through it before\non my continent,"},{"time":925465,"text":"and I am very clear about that.\""},{"time":928175,"text":"So he was not going to,\njust for political expediency,"},{"time":932160,"text":"embrace the, kind of, lowest\ncommon denominator"},{"time":935626,"text":"that had been embraced\nin other political elections."},{"time":939655,"text":"And he stood against Marine Le Pen,\nwho is a very dangerous woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944928,"text":"CH: Last question for you, Christiane."},{"time":948093,"text":"Tell us about ideas worth spreading."},{"time":950115,"text":"If you could plant one idea\ninto the minds of everyone here,"},{"time":954786,"text":"what would that be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":956007,"text":"CA: I would say really be careful\nwhere you get your information from;"},{"time":961145,"text":"really take responsibility\nfor what you read, listen to and watch;"},{"time":966491,"text":"make sure that you go to the trusted\nbrands to get your main information,"},{"time":971402,"text":"no matter whether you have\na wide, eclectic intake,"},{"time":976115,"text":"really stick with the brand\nnames that you know,"},{"time":979134,"text":"because in this world right now,\nat this moment right now,"},{"time":982750,"text":"our crises, our challenges,\nour problems are so severe,"},{"time":987113,"text":"that unless we are all engaged\nas global citizens"},{"time":990688,"text":"who appreciate the truth,"},{"time":992615,"text":"who understand science,\nempirical evidence and facts,"},{"time":996984,"text":"then we are just simply\ngoing to be wandering along"},{"time":1000507,"text":"to a potential catastrophe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002492,"text":"So I would say, the truth,"},{"time":1003880,"text":"and then I would come back\nto Emmanuel Macron"},{"time":1006160,"text":"and talk about love."},{"time":1008022,"text":"I would say that there's not\nenough love going around."},{"time":1012515,"text":"And I asked him to tell me about love."},{"time":1015231,"text":"I said, \"You know, your marriage\nis the subject of global obsession.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018847,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020506,"text":"\"Can you tell me about love?"},{"time":1021943,"text":"What does it mean to you?\""},{"time":1023281,"text":"I've never asked a president\nor an elected leader about love."},{"time":1026246,"text":"I thought I'd try it."},{"time":1027428,"text":"And he said -- you know,\nhe actually answered it."},{"time":1031367,"text":"And he said, \"I love my wife,\nshe is part of me,"},{"time":1035552,"text":"we've been together for decades.\""},{"time":1037203,"text":"But here's where it really counted,"},{"time":1038912,"text":"what really stuck with me."},{"time":1040439,"text":"He said,"},{"time":1041704,"text":"\"It is so important for me\nto have somebody at home"},{"time":1045248,"text":"who tells me the truth.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048618,"text":"So you see, I brought it home.\nIt's all about the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1051354,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052384,"text":"CH: So there you go. Truth and love.\nIdeas worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1055215,"text":"Christiane Amanpour, thank you\nso much. That was great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1057902,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1058994,"text":"CA: Thank you.\nCH: That was really lovely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1061352,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062591,"text":"CA: Thank you."}]}]}